{"type":"message","id":"926fe031","parentId":"5a47a0ab","timestamp":"2026-03-29T11:02:52.794Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-03-29 19:02 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 请完成以下自主学习任务（完成后自动退出）：\n\n1. 搜索企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务等道简网络相关行业的最新动态（2026年3月）\n2. 整理3-5条关键信息，每条包含：标题、来源、摘要、启示\n3. 将结果保存到 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md\n\n请使用网络搜索工具搜索相关信息，整理后写入文件。"}],"timestamp":1774782172790}}
{"type":"message","id":"69aa47af","parentId":"926fe031","timestamp":"2026-03-29T11:03:00.103Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to search for the latest news about enterprise digital transformation, intelligent security, network system integration, and IT operations services related to 道简网络's industry in March 2026. I need to find 3-5 key pieces of information and save them to a file.\n\nLet me first check the miaoda-web-search skill to understand how to search for information.","thinkingSignature":"0c9cca63bf8bbe4e22aa84fcfc0abda26ed6a9771a0c4b58dfdece6398e4a06d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kj717ul8mb6g_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"~/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":117,"output":117,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":42112,"totalTokens":42346,"cost":{"input":0.0000351,"output":0.0001404,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.005053439999999999,"total":0.00522894}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774782172792}}
{"type":"message","id":"f7f25a5f","parentId":"69aa47af","timestamp":"2026-03-29T11:03:00.112Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_kj717ul8mb6g_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774782180108}}
{"type":"message","id":"2fd7703b","parentId":"f7f25a5f","timestamp":"2026-03-29T11:03:03.882Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to search for information about enterprise digital transformation, intelligent security, network system integration, and IT operations services in March 2026. Let me run several searches in parallel.","thinkingSignature":"10e6d5dc5068ec2c83e3949ede56505272b7c0c9552495151e173022282278d9"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rhtseuiy9r9l_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026年3月 最新动态 政策\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rhtseuiy9r9l_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防 2026年3月 行业动态\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rhtseuiy9r9l_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 IT运维服务 2026年3月 行业趋势\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":911,"output":166,"cacheRead":41950,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43027,"cost":{"input":0.0002733,"output":0.0001992,"cacheRead":0.0012584999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001731}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774782180111}}
